overview.en: GSENetwork aims to build a transparent and secure network designed for decentralized economies. Leveraging on IoT technology, blockchain-powered incentivization, a two-asset price stability mechanism and robust smart contracts, GSENetwork aims to be a deeply scalable token ecosystem that encourages high performance recording of on-chain sharing transactions, bringing real-world trust into the digital world.
overview.zh: GSENetwork致力于建立一个透明安全的现象级去中心化信用网络，借助物联网技术、通证激励体系、复合通证经济设计及智能合约服务，由共享经济切入实现信用上链，为中心化服务（DService）提供底层区块链平台，重新定义古典共享经济中参与者的生产关系。
